text: Zheng Wushuang (; ; born 29 November 1998) is a Chinese female tennis player. She has a career-high WTA singles ranking of 430, achieved on 24 February 2020. On 9 September 2019, she peaked at No. 309 in the WTA doubles rankings. On the ITF Junior Circuit, Zheng has a combined career-high juniors ranking of 13, reached in January 2016.
